ution of lube base oil bitumenasphalt and other byproducts as well as special products such as treated distillate aromatics extract and slack wax operation of  megawatts  megawatts and  megawatts of electricity power plants generation of steam marine transportation of petroleum and petrochemical products through tankers and petroleum transportation through multiproduct pipeline and production and sale of sugarcane cassavabased and molassesbased ethanol in addition the company invests manufactures and distributes hydrocarbon solvents chemical solvents and other chemicals manufactures and sells linear alkyl benzene and other related products and provides marine transportation services for crew and utilities as well as management and general services further it provides consultancy services in the area of energyrelated and petrochemical businesses thai oil public company limited is headquartered in bangkok thailand top  rankings search year                region americas asiapacific rim emea industry coal and consumable fuels electric utilities gas utilities independent power producers and energy traders integrated oil and gas multiutilities oil and gas exploration and production oil and gas refining and marketing oil and gas storage and transportation select year  rankings rankings highlights contact us about top  rankings site map privacy policy plattscom   sp global platts a division of sp global all rights reserved